activateStrategy().notice: Activate the current strategy set for the vault.

deposit().notice: Handles deposits from the liquidity pool

getTotalUnderlying().notice: Computes the total underlying of the vault: idle funds + allocated funds

harvest().details: Harvesting adds profits to the vault's balance and deducts fees.  No performance fees are charged on profit used to repay debt.
harvest().notice: Harvest profits from the vault's strategy.

initializeStrategy(address).details: Bypasses the time delay, but can only be called if strategy is not set already.

shutdownStrategy().notice: Shuts down the strategy, withdraws all funds from vault and strategy and transfer them to the pool.

updateBound(uint256).notice: Update deviation bound for strategy allocation.

params.bound_: New deviation bound for target allocation.

updateStrategistFee(uint256).notice: Update strategist fee (with time delay enforced).

updateStrategy(address).notice: Update the vault's strategy (with time delay enforced).

withdraw(uint256).details: If the specified amount exceeds idle funds, an amount of funds is withdrawn      from the strategy such that it will achieve a target allocation for after the      amount has been withdrawn.
withdraw(uint256).notice: Withdraws specified amount of underlying from vault.

withdrawAllFromStrategy().details: Harvests profits before withdrawing. Deactivates strategy after withdrawing.
withdrawAllFromStrategy().notice: Withdraws all funds from strategy to vault.

withdrawAvailableToPool().notice: Transfers all the available funds to the pool

withdrawFromReserve(uint256).details: Withdraws from reserve will cause a spike in pool exchange rate.  Pool deposits should be paused during this to prevent front running

withdrawFromStrategy(uint256).notice: Withdraws an amount of underlying from the strategy to the vault.
